leve.name: One Big Problem Solved
leve.description: In the name of the Maelstrom, slay the gigas who threaten the dig at Silvertear Falls. These hulking creatures have traveled all the way from Abalathia's Spine to wreak havoc on the naturalists of Saint Coinach's Find, they of uneasy discoveries and strange accidents. Ask not why the gigas cameâ”€kill them, for science!
